=======================================================
Program (C Code)
=======================================================
void main() {
    int T1 = 1, T2, T3;

    while(1) {
        T2 = 1 + T1;
        T3 = T1 + 1;
    }
}


=======================================================
Explanation
=======================================================
Here after the second instruction in the while loop
T2 and T3 must be equivalent.
